{"type":null,"faqId":32678,"title":"连接电脑热点（猎豹、360）共享热点概率断开连接怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">一、请您将电脑驱动升级到最新版本；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">二、配置电脑网卡适配手机WLAN：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">    1、打开网络和共享中心，选择电脑无线网卡，点击配置</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">    2、修改AP兼容性的值为更广泛的兼容性</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">    3、将WMM功能禁用</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">    4、禁用802.11n模式</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">    5、将与40MHZ信道不兼容值设置为已启用</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">更详细设置可以参考：http://tieba.baidu.com/p/3366224615。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7380","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748379000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":11,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"360WIFI,电脑热点,猎豹,断开","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}